<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <title>Obnova hesla</title>
    <style>
    body, #msg {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #444349;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    #msg {
        background-color: #FFF;
        width: 80%;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px auto 50px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        overflow: hidden;
        -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
        -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    #msg-content {
        padding: 20px 40px 40px;
    }
    #msg-content p {
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 6px 0 8px;
    }

    #headline {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 0 0px;

        padding: 22px 40px 20px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: normal;

        color: #888;
        background-color: #F2F2F2;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #EEE;
    }
    #headline p {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    #headline b {
        font-weight: normal;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="msg">
    <div id="headline"><b>Obnova hesla</b></div>
    <div id="msg-content">
        <p>Dobrý den,<br>
        kliknutím na následující odkaz si můžete změnit heslo.</p>
        <p><a n:href="//User:PasswordRequest (expand) $request">{link //User:PasswordRequest (expand) $request}</a></p>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>